 rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = timed out waiting for server handshake\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"17004f02-74c1-4444-9be1-b2e134544a72\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"e3701923-f30f-4b62-92b0-f0e0a40b8f66\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-05T20:30:38.16210821Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-07,frontend,frontend-1,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = failed to charge card: could not charge the card: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: i/o timeout\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"9493c2a8-63fb-460c-91c4-73803b27304c\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"366859a6-2f48-493d-85f9-e2d3dec270cb\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-05T20:32:26.77861075Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-2", "frontend-1", "frontend-0"], "service_name": ["frontend"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-07", "aiops-k8s-03"]}, "matched_anomaly": "Please analyze the abnormal event between 2025-06-05T20:10:09Z and 2025-06-05T20:34:09Z and provide the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-05 20:10:09+00:00 to 2025-06-05 20:34:09+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "根据获取到的日志数据，我已经完成了对异常时间段的初始扫描分析。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"timeout\", \"i/o timeout\", \"timed out waiting for server handshake\", \"connection error\", \"transport\", \"Error while dialing\", \"context canceled\", \"Unavailable\", \"Internal\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"支付服务出现连接超时和握手超时问题，导致frontend服务无法完成订单支付流程\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend服务报告'failed to charge card: could not charge the card: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = timed out waiting for server handshake'和'transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: i/o timeout'\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"前端服务在调用支付服务时出现超时和连接错误，部分请求因context canceled而中断\",\n      \"evidence\": \"多个frontend实例报告相同的支付服务连接问题，包括'context canceled'错误\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析总结\n\n**关键发现：**\n1. **主要异常模式**：所有错误都来自frontend服务，集中在订单支付流程（/cart/checkout路径）\n2. **核心问题**：frontend服务无法连接到paymentservice（IP: 10.233.55.4:50051）\n3. **错误类型**：\n   - 连接超时（i/o timeout）\n   - 握手超时（timed out waiting for server handshake）\n   - 上下文取消（context canceled）\n\n**初步判断**：\n- paymentservice可能是根因组件，因为所有frontend实例都报告相同的连接问题\n- 需要进一步检查paymentservice的健康状态和网络连接配置\n- 可能涉及网络分区、服务负载过高或配置错误等问题\n\n当前处于初始扫描阶段，建议下一步深入分析paymentservice的日志和监控指标来确认根因。", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于对异常时间段 2025-06-05T20:10:09Z 至 2025-06-05T20:34:09Z 的调用链数据分析，我已完成初始扫描并识别出显著的异常调用链。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PaymentService/Charge 操作延迟从正常 12.8ms 激增至 24,427ms（延迟倍数 1,904倍），出现43次异常，状态码显示连接超时和握手超时\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CheckoutService/PlaceOrder 操作延迟从正常 145-159ms 激增至 22-30秒，所有frontend实例调用checkoutservice均出现超时和取消错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"前端服务HTTP 500错误频发，主要由于下游checkoutservice调用失败，出现大量上下文取消和超时错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"ShippingService/GetQuote 延迟从正常200ms增至600ms，虽然影响相对较小，但表明checkoutservice调用链整体受影响\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"ProductCatalogService/GetProduct 延迟从正常9-10ms增至11-19ms，轻微延迟表明系统整体性能下降\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现分析：\n\n**根因定位**：PaymentService是问题根源\n- PaymentService/Charge操作出现最严重的延迟（1,904倍增长）\n- 错误信息显示连接超时：\"dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: i/o timeout\"\n- 这是调用链中最下游的异常服务，其他服务异常都是其受害者\n\n**错误传播路径**：\n```\nPaymentService（根因）→ CheckoutService（受害者）→ Frontend（受害者）\n```\n\n**异常特征**：\n- **严重延迟**：PaymentService响应时间从毫秒级激增至秒级\n- **连接失败**：网络连接超时和握手超时错误\n- **级联故障**：下游故障导致上游服务大量上下文取消和超时\n\n建议进一步检查PaymentService的健康状态、网络连接性和资源使用情况。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的监控数据，我现在对异常事件进行初步分析。以下是全面扫描的结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max 和 rrt 指标出现严重性能退化，rrt_max 从正常 199453 飙升至 20122078.5，变化率高达 1960.7%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice-2 的 rrt_max 从 199453.0 升至 20122078.5，rrt 从 6940.76 升至 539988.77\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max 和 rrt 指标显著异常，同时 error_ratio 和 server_error_ratio 出现错误率上升\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-2 的 rrt_max 从 212274.0 升至 14046338.0，error_ratio 从 0.0 升至 0.09\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max 和 rrt 性能严重下降，server_error_ratio 出现错误率异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-1 的 rrt_max 从 252690.0 升至 20126514.5，server_error_ratio 从 0.0 升至 0.19\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max 性能显著退化，虽然 error_ratio 保持 0.0 但 p99 值出现异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0 的 rrt_max 从 248283.0 升至 20064311.0，error_ratio p99 从 0.0 升至 1.13\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt 和 rrt_max 的 p99 值出现极端异常，p99 变化率接近 2000%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"paymentservice-0 的 rrt p99 从 2127.52 升至 2472178.23，rrt_max p99 从 3260.76 升至 2543459.37\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"client_error_ratio 的 p99 值出现严重异常，从 0.0 升至 26.52\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice-1 的 client_error_ratio p99 从 0.0 升至 26.52，虽然中位数保持 0.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"client_error_ratio 的 p99 值异常升高，从 0.0 升至 26.87\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice-2 的 client_error_ratio p99 从 0.0 升至 26.87，中位数保持 0.0\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 初步发现总结：\n\n**关键异常模式**：\n1. **严重性能退化**：多个服务的 `rrt_max` 和 `rrt` 指标出现极端异常，变化率普遍超过 1900%\n2. **错误率上升**：frontend 服务的 `error_ratio` 和 `server_error_ratio` 出现异常\n3. **客户端错误**：cartservice 的 `client_error_ratio` p99 值显著升高\n\n**影响范围**：\n- 主要影响前端服务（frontend-0,1,2）和 checkoutservice-2\n- paymentservice-0 出现极端 p99 延迟异常\n- cartservice 出现客户端错误率异常\n\n**下一步分析方向**：需要进一步分析这些服务之间的调用关系，确定故障传播路径和根因服务。"}
